data.text:
An R&B unit consisting of SAKI, IZUMI, and MARLEY who made their debut from the original soundtrack of the blockbuster drama “Long Vacation,” which left a mark in TV history with the highest audience rating of 36.7%, starring Takuya Kimura, Tomoko Yamaguchi, and Yutaka Takenouchi. , Section-S’s first album is the long-awaited first LP!

A masterpiece containing many of the monumental songs of 90’s Japanese R&B. Produced by CAGNET/Daisuke Hinata. Released in 1996.
